  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study was designed to explore the clinical effect of magnetic field
      modulation system on insomnia patients and provide a new solution for insomnia treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with insomnia receiving this sleep pillow with magnetic system or not would be
      observed in months.The effect of sleep pillow with magnetic system for insomnia would
      evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
